OL,7,FFor young people it can be hard to
OL,8,Funderstand the struggles of elderly
OL,9,Fpeople to do even the most basic tasks,
OL,10,Fso Spanish students designed a special
OL,11,Fsuit to recreate the experience of life
OL,12,Ffor octogenarians.
OL,14,FAndrea Lucena Perea and Yipsy Perez
OL,15,FTorres, both 26, were part of a team at
OL,16,Fthe University of Granada which
OL,17,Fdesigned the black suit to bridge the
OL,18,Fgap in understanding between different
OL,19,Fgenerations.
OL,3,C'I felt trapped and overwhelmed': What
OL,4,Cit feels like to wear a suit that
OL,5,Cstimulates old age
